casebody.data:
Brett WEICHERS, Plaintiff-Appellee,
v.
BOURBON STREET BAR & GRILL, INC., d/b/a Bourbon Street Bar & Grill and Voodoo Lounge, and D-Squared, LLC, d/b/a Whiskey Road, Defendants,
and
Monkey, Inc., d/b/a Tony's La Pizzeria, Defendant-Appellant. No. 17-1960 Court of Appeals of Iowa. Filed February 6, 2019

DECISION WITHOUT PUBLISHED OPINION

See Iowa R. App. P. 6.904

Monkey, Inc., d/b/a Tony's La Pizzeria, appeals the district court's denial of its motion for summary judgment. REVERSED AND REMANDED.

REVERSED. REMANDED.
